reviewText: From the trailer looks like a good urban movie I will purchase when it becomes digital

I just had to show some love and respect to the homie jiwe morris this movie was well put together and had a good message on some real s*** for $25 it was worth it ...a lot of people don't understand gang life ..I do because I been there back in the day I repped G-shine family on the east side so I understand why people join ,bang,and there beliefs and mindset but on some trill shyte its not worth it all it gets you is prison,dead,pain yes you can make a few good friends but long run no good
The ending could of been better
This movie concept was understandable about the urban life iin Newark. But the quality of this movie is not worth 25,00USD. It should of been posted on you tube for free.

Hope y'all can appreciate and understand why I did this film. Its bigger than violence and sets but resolution, respect, and the value of human life.
